_json.description: Laura Ashley’s second Tea Room offers one of the best afternoon teas near Windsor. Tucked away in Buckinghamshire’s countryside, The Tea Room opened its doors at Burnham Beeches Hotel in July 2018 and offers its guests a truly magnificent experience. Draped from floor to ceiling in stunning Laura Ashley design, with large windows offering beautiful views over the hotel grounds, The Tea Room offers an experience like no other.
